name: Thescriptbank
tagline: A place where all scripts come to rest.
body:
Welcome to the Script Bank.

We will be logging all scripts here for as long as we have time and the will to want to do so. If you see a script that isn't here, and updated, please let us know and we will add it.

Enjoy.

Report everything in this thread: http://www.gamekiller.net/threads/ce-scripts-the-script-bank.3241020/
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
